Oh, ow! Damn it!

You bitch!
Ugh, dicks!

Freakin' ow!

Man, I'm even a hot piece of ass as a gun! I mean, look at these bevels! Damn!
This is -- this is great. We make a great pair. Which is to say, I'm great, you look great holding me. But it's -- it's really great.

Hey, where we goin' after this? I don't know about you, but I could murder some sushi right now.
